 hundred Muslims at his funeral, he will be forgiven.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1488 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11334,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/11\/visit-graves-reminder\/","url_meta":{"origin":36772,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Graves: Permission to visit graves as a reminder","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, visited the grave of his mother and he wept and made others around him start weeping. The Prophet said, \u201cI asked my Lord for permission to seek forgiveness for her and He did not give me permission, then I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2780,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/05\/janazah-prophet-najashi-negus\/","url_meta":{"origin":36772,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Najashi: The Prophet prays funeral prayer for King of Abyssinia","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, told us about the Negus, the ruler of Abyssinia, on the day he died. The Prophet said to us, \u201cSeek forgiveness for your brother.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1263, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 951 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40501,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/07\/only-those-forgiven\/","url_meta":{"origin":36772,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Death: Only those forgiven rest in peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Bilal stood for the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cThis person has died and now is resting in peace.\u201d The Prophet was upset by that, and he said, \u201cVerily, only those forgiven rest in peace.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 9379 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32675,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/05\/prophet-dua-at-janazah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36772,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Janaza